parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inadequate headlight performance can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Dim or weak headlights
inadequate illumination of the road
poor visibility
difficulty seeing pedestrians or objects
inability to see road signs or street markers
and reduced safety while driving at night.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, making it challenging to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the vehicle vibrates or shakes
the power steering assist message is displayed
the vehicle loses power steering
and the vehicle becomes hard to steer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of power steering and power braking, which can result in accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The fuel filter warning light comes on
the engine stalls
the vehicle loses power steering and power braking
and the vehicle becomes difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive tire wear can lead to reduced traction, increased stopping distances, and loss of control, which can cause accidents.
symptoms: The front tires wear excessively on the outside edge
the vehicle pulls to one side
and the tires need to be replaced frequently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause the vehicle to vibrate or shake, making it challenging to control, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates or shakes
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
and the vehicle becomes hard to steer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Poor visibility due to inadequate headlight performance can increase the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: The low beam headlight provides poor visibility
making it difficult to see the road ahead.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various issues, including distracted driving, loss of critical vehicle functions, and potentially, accidents.
symptoms: Constant loud chime and visual warning
communications quit working
hands-free phone feature not working
electrical dashboard flicker and shutdown
instrument panel dimming
headlights failure to illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the trailer brake system can cause decreased braking performance, potentially leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Service trailer brake system warning
constant loud chime and visual warning
decreased braking of the trailer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the horn can cause a lack of warning to other drivers, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: No sound coming from the horn when pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear window defrost can cause reduced visibility, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Rear window fracture
smoke and fire from the rear of the vehicle.
